      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Dennis Breuker</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:272px;\"><a href=\"http://www.dennisbreuker.nl\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/7/7c/Dennis_Breuker-20160519-vierkant.png\" width=\"270\" height=\"270\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Dennis_Breuker-20160519-vierkant.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Dennis Breuker <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Dennis M. Breuker</b>,<br />\na Dutch computer and games scientist. He defended his <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Master%27s_degree\">M.Sc.</a> at the Computer Science Department of the <a href=\"/Leiden_University\" title=\"Leiden University\">Leiden University</a> and his <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Doctor_of_Philosophy\">Ph.D.</a> at the Computer Science Department of the <a href=\"/Maastricht_University\" title=\"Maastricht University\">Maastricht University</a>, where he was author and co-author of various papers with focus on <a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">search algorithms</a>, the utilization of the <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a> and <a href=\"/Graph_History_Interaction\" title=\"Graph History Interaction\">Graph History Interaction</a> (GHI). <i>Memory versus Search in Games</i> is the title of his Ph.D. thesis <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> , a <a href=\"/Recommended_Reading\" title=\"Recommended Reading\">recommended reading</a> for every chess programmer. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Programs\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Programs</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#1992_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1992 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Programs\">Programs</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dennis_Breuker&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Programs\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>Dennis is author of the chess program <a href=\"/Duck\" title=\"Duck\">Duck</a>, already written during his studies in Leiden, with later improvements when he was in Maastricht. As co-author of the <a href=\"/Othello\" title=\"Othello\">Othello</a> program <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/program.php?id=285\">Aida</a>, Dennis Breuker won the silver medal during the <a href=\"/4th_Computer_Olympiad#Othello\" title=\"4th Computer Olympiad\">4th Computer Olympiad 1992</a> in London <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> . A further chess program by Dennis Breuker, <a href=\"/AliBaba\" title=\"AliBaba\">AliBaba</a>, was written for testing various hashing algorithms - with the permission of the author, a modified version is available from <a href=\"/Dann_Corbit\" title=\"Dann Corbit\">Dann Corbit's</a> site <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> and was adopted to <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">WinBoard</a> by <a href=\"/Jim_Ablett\" title=\"Jim Ablett\">Jim Ablett</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> .\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dennis_Breuker&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1992_...\">1992 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dennis_Breuker&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 1992 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dennis Breuker</a>, <a href=\"/Victor_Allis\" title=\"Victor Allis\">Victor Allis</a>, <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a>, <a href=\"/Bob_Herschberg\" title=\"Bob Herschberg\">Bob Herschberg</a> (<b>1992</b>). <i>A Database as a Second.</i> <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#15_1\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICCA Journal, Vol. 15, No. 1</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dennis Breuker</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jacco_Gnodde&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jacco Gnodde (page does not exist)\">Jacco Gnodde</a> (<b>1992</b>). <i>The AST 4th Computer Olympiad</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#15_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICCA Journal, Vol. 15, No. 3</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/4th_Computer_Olympiad\" title=\"4th Computer Olympiad\">4th Computer Olympiad</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dennis Breuker</a>, <a href=\"/Jos_Uiterwijk\" title=\"Jos Uiterwijk\">Jos Uiterwijk</a> (<b>1992</b>). <i>The 12th Dutch Computer-Chess Championship</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#15_4\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICCA Journal, Vol. 15, No. 4</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/DOCCC_1992\" title=\"DOCCC 1992\">DOCCC 1992</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dennis Breuker</a>, <a href=\"/Victor_Allis\" title=\"Victor Allis\">Victor Allis</a>, <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a> (<b>1994</b>). <i>How to Mate: Applying Proof-Number Search</i>. <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Chess_7\" title=\"Advances in Computer Chess 7\">Advances in Computer Chess 7</a>, reprint as <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.top-5000.nl/ps/Mate%20in%2038-%20applying%20proof%20number%20search%20to%20chess.pdf\">Mate in 38: Applying Proof-Number Search</a> from <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schröder's</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.top-5000.nl/prostuff.htm\">Programmer's Stuff site</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dennis Breuker</a>, <a href=\"/Jos_Uiterwijk\" title=\"Jos Uiterwijk\">Jos Uiterwijk</a>, <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a> (<b>1994</b>). <i>Replacement Schemes for Transposition Tables</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#17_4\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICCA Journal, Vol. 17, No. 4</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dennis Breuker</a>, <a href=\"/Jos_Uiterwijk\" title=\"Jos Uiterwijk\">Jos Uiterwijk</a>, <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a> (<b>1996</b>). <i>Replacement Schemes and Two-Level Tables.</i> <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#19_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICCA Journal, Vol. 19, No. 3</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dennis Breuker</a>, <a href=\"/Jos_Uiterwijk\" title=\"Jos Uiterwijk\">Jos Uiterwijk</a>, <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a> (<b>1997</b>). <i>Information in Transposition Tables</i>. <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Chess_8\" title=\"Advances in Computer Chess 8\">Advances in Computer Chess 8</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dennis Breuker</a> (<b>1998</b>). <i>Memory versus Search in Games</i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a href=\"/Maastricht_University\" title=\"Maastricht University\">Maastricht University</a>, pdf via <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.dennisbreuker.nl/thesis/index.html\">Dennis Breuker's page</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://www.dennisbreuker.nl/thesis/index.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"MemoryVersusSearchcover5x7.jpg\" src=\"/images/3/30/MemoryVersusSearchcover5x7.jpg\" width=\"142\" height=\"199\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Dap_Hartmann\" title=\"Dap Hartmann\">Dap Hartmann</a> (<b>1998</b>). <i><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dennis Breuker</a>: Memory versus Search in Games</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#21_4\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICCA Journal, Vol. 21, No. 4</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dennis Breuker</a>, <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a>, <a href=\"/Jos_Uiterwijk\" title=\"Jos Uiterwijk\">Jos Uiterwijk</a>, <a href=\"/Victor_Allis\" title=\"Victor Allis\">Victor Allis</a> (<b>1998</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/3-540-48957-6_3\">A Solution to the GHI Problem for Best-First Search</a></i>. <a href=\"/CG_1998\" title=\"CG 1998\">CG 1998</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dennis_Breuker&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dennis Breuker</a>, <a href=\"/Jos_Uiterwijk\" title=\"Jos Uiterwijk\">Jos Uiterwijk</a>, <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i>Solving 8 × 8 Domineering</i>. Theoretical Computer Science, Vol. 230, pp. 195-206. ISSN 0304-3975.</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dennis Breuker</a>, <a href=\"/Jos_Uiterwijk\" title=\"Jos Uiterwijk\">Jos Uiterwijk</a>, <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a> (<b>2001</b>). <i>The PN2-Search Algorithm</i>. <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Games_9\" title=\"Advances in Computer Games 9\">Advances in Computer Games 9</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dennis Breuker</a>, <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a>, <a href=\"/Jos_Uiterwijk\" title=\"Jos Uiterwijk\">Jos Uiterwijk</a>, <a href=\"/Victor_Allis\" title=\"Victor Allis\">Victor Allis</a> (<b>2001</b>). <i>A Solution to the GHI Problem for Best-First Search</i>. Theoretical Computer Science, Vol. 252, Nos. 1-2, pp. 121-149.</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dennis_Breuker&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.dennisbreuker.nl/\">Dennis Breuker's Homepage</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/person.php?id=286\">Dennis Breuker's ICGA Tournaments</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://genealogy.math.ndsu.nodak.edu/id.php?id=140423\">The Mathematics Genealogy Project - Dennis Breuker</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.othello.dk/book/index.php/Dennis_Breuker\">Dennis Breuker - The Othello Wiki Book Project</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dennis_Breuker&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.dennisbreuker.nl/\">Dennis Breuker's Homepage</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dennis Breuker</a> (<b>1998</b>). <i>Memory versus Search in Games</i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a href=\"/Maastricht_University\" title=\"Maastricht University\">Maastricht University</a>, pdf via <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.dennisbreuker.nl/thesis/index.html\">Dennis Breuker's page</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/person.php?id=286\">Dennis Breuker's ICGA Tournaments</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-b